{
  "stem": "4963.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my parents didn't want us to-- summertime was just when school was over.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I was very insistent on going to summer camp, so they finally consented to let me go for two weeks.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I left on a Sunday, and on a Tuesday, the-- they were sent out to Siberia, the whole family-- my mother and father and two sisters.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they uncovered there, the secret police came in at night and lined up my parents against the wall and told my mother to take whatever she wanted, that they were just-- they were just moving them to another-- to another country-- to another city.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so I was away in camp in Palanga, which was a-- by the seashore.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would say it was about 30 miles from Kovno.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I didn't know anything about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- so this was Tuesday night, and they were placed in-- in animal wagons, cars, trains.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were there at the station, from what I understand, for about two days.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My father, in turn, was separated from my mother and two sisters.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my mother was-- both of my parents were really remarkable, but especially my mother because you can imagine the feelings she had.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean here she had a two-year-old and a seven-year-old with her.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "One daughter, a 10-year-old or 11-year-old, was away in the summer camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My father was in another cart.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they were just treated terribly without food, without any water.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I remember, my aunt-- but they were permitted to have the family come.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So my my-- and my Aunt Paula and Chassia, my-- my father's sisters, would come-- would come there and, you know, bring them food, and water, and so on.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
